{
    semantic: {
        'b': 'strong',
        'i': 'em',
        's': 'del',
        'strike': 'del',
        'div': 'div'

    tagsToKeep: [
      "area",
      "base",
      "br",

      "source",

    autogrow: true,

        ["viewHTML"],
        ["undo", "redo"],
        ["heading", "paragraph", "fontSize"],

        ["foreColor", "backColor"],
        ["links"],
        ["image"],
        ["align"],
        ["list", "bulletList", "numberList"],
        ["sectionBreak"],
        ["removeformat"],
        ["fullscreen"],
        ["accordion"],
        ["tabs"]
    ],
    btnsDef: {
        align: {
            dropdown: ["justifyLeft", "justifyCenter", "justifyRight", "justifyFull"],
